36:08.633 --> 36:13.071 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
CHARLAYNE HUNTER-GAULT: We
caught up with
Reverend Billings at one of his
organization's

36:13.171 --> 36:18.243 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
