36:22.881 --> 36:26.017 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
CHARLAYNE HUNTER-GAULT: The
institute has
conducted over a half-million
workshops with

36:26.117 --> 36:31.556 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
