people coming
to you or fewer?

41:23.981 --> 41:25.883 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
REV. DAVID BILLINGS: Yes, we are
getting more.

41:25.983 --> 41:32.890 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
But I -- I hear your question.
It's usually,
like, people will say, well,
you're speaking

41:32.990 --> 41:38.696 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
