stay hopeful
to do this work.

41:58.249 --> 42:00.051 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
CHARLAYNE HUNTER-GAULT: So,
what's the solution?

42:00.151 --> 42:03.020 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
REV. DAVID BILLINGS: You have
got to keep
the work going. You have got to
transfer it.

42:03.121 --> 42:10.361 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
