we're talking
a brother and sister.

42:28.179 --> 42:35.052 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Well, those children are --
could be -- you
know, will understand race. They
will understand

42:35.153 --> 42:41.159 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
